Hideaway;;1995;;R;;Fantasy,Horror,Thriller;;5.3;;Brett Leonard;;Jeff Goldblum,Christine Lahti,Alicia Silverstone,Jeremy Sisto,Alfred Molina,Rae Dawn Chong,Kenneth Welsh,Saraphina Joachim,Shirley Broderick,Tom McBeath,Joely Collins,Roger Cross,Michael McDonald,Don S. Davis,Rebecca Toolan,Hiro Kanagawa,Jayme Knox,Norma Jean Wick;;Hatch Harrison had a traffic accident with his car. At first the doctors said he was dead but then they succeeded in bringing him back to life after two hours. In no time, Hatch starts to have strange sensations and discovers that he is now united with a mad killer who had entered his mind during his death.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113303/